snippet.title: Robot Wants Kitty (for iPhone)
snippet.description: A robot's life is cold, mechanical and unfeeling. So what is a poor robot to do? Robot needs life, companionship, and something to warm Robot's lonely steel heart. And Robot is willing to use lasers to get it! Robot wants Kitty!
